item.title: How do you go directly to world in mozilla or ie
item.dc:creator: @frank frank_
item.description:
@frank wrote:

Last i looked, the applet tags are written into the page by javascript, so you will need it enabled, you can however, use javascript injection to do “directly” to the game page
egjavascript:void(frames[0].location.href="http://uk4.runescape.com/lang/en/aff/runescape/game.ws?lowmem=1&plugin=0");
Edit: if you dont know how to do javascript injection; all you have to do is stick that in the address bar and hit enter.

Dont forget, there IS a difference between java, and java script. You need to disabled java script.
